description: Not to demerit or offend any other point of view, I am just textualizing and externalizing a part of my belief and thoughts in a Word paragraph while listening to jazz and watching relaxing landscapes that I am not paying attention to, I am only one person sharing the chaos of his ideas in a set of computer algorithms are global relevance that only serves to awaken my unconscious self and to open my mind without thinking too much to write what happens in my psyche, I do not over think, nor analyze what I say, I just let my hands write this and then I am only motivated by the realization that I love my own way of seeing the world ...
